              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/13339770/" class="">译者的话</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1903629/" class=" " title="Null">Null</a>
                (但念无常，慎勿放逸)
              
